Class RawDataSourceImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • nz.co.pltech.arda.engine.api.builder.RawDataSource
      • com.intel.fightclub.coach.RawDataSourceImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    nz.co.pltech.arda.engine.api.builder.EngineDataSource

    @NotThreadSafe
public final class RawDataSourceImpl
extends nz.co.pltech.arda.engine.api.builder.RawDataSource
    Implementation of RawDataSource class for feeding incomplete data to ARDA. Currently, its EngineData.EngineDataBuilder requires certain data types that FC's device is not planning to provide, so we will have ARDA generate those. An example is power, we will have ARDA generate power metrics through its interface.
